Brings out the best in his crews and ships.

<color=#309BBF>Extremist</color>
Uses all available means to gain an advantage.

<color=#309BBF>Overseer</color>
Targets his opponent''s most valuable assets while protecting his own.', '2025-08-13 17:11:38');
